# Migrations and Models

- Always create Alembic migrations for schema changes
- Use UUID primary keys for all entities
- Use UTC timestamps (`DateTime(timezone=True)`)
- Include audit fields (`created_by_id`, `updated_by_id`)
- Support soft delete via `deleted_at` column
- Every feature that changes schema MUST update documentation
